Relationship to Reality_Engine
------------------------------
Ursprung is a standalone downstream consumer of the Reality_Engine (Chronicle/Dentatus)
workbench. Per the workbench's "Sibling Law", Ursprung imports the workbench read-only
(see ursprung/_workbench.py) and never edits, vendors, or relicenses any workbench file.
The workbench is the verification substrate; Ursprung is the renderer. integrity != truth.
